                  <summary change="#add-summary">
                     1 copy of Nuzhat al-khāṭir wa-surūr al-nāḍir by Fakhr al-Dīn ibn Muḥammad Ṭarīḥ ibn ʿAlī al-Najafī, d. 1085/1674
